 ('2', '3', 'en_us', NULL, '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Crafttest.dev. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-06-21 23:58:55', '2013-06-21 23:58:55', 'cdef9cdc-c03a-4347-af83-e5ed45f315a9'),
